#<AdxTL>@(#)0.0.0.0 $Revision$ 
$ACTION
Case ACTION
   When "OUVRE"       : Gosub OUVRE
   When "DEBUT"       : Gosub DEBUT
Endcase

Return

$OUVRE
Gosub OUVRE_OUT From ESSCHDAV
#Manage Localisations
Call MANAGE_LOCALISATION("ESSCHDV") From DIVPAYE

Return

$DEBUT
Gosub DEBUT_OUT From ESSCHDAV
#Manage localisations
Call HIDE_ACTIVITYFIELDS From WESSCHDVHIDE
Call SHOW_LEGACTCALLS From WESSCHDVSHOW
Affzo [M:ESCHD]1-99
Return




